author: Screen Junkies
description:
It's the Honest Trailer for Captain America: New World Order! I mean— Brave New World! Finally see Sam Wilson take on the mantle of Captain America, assuming you skipped the Disney Plus series where he did exactly that! Finally see Harrison Ford play a fictional president...who is also a Hulk! Is it good? Depends on what you're comparing it to. Somewhere between The Eternals and a flat room temp Diet Coke on the enjoyment scale. And that's the current-phase MCU promise.

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)
